# Modern Cutlist Optimizer

Build a modern, high-performance 2D cutlist optimizer using React and Vite. The application will help woodworkers and makers calculate the most efficient way to cut panels from stock sheets, minimizing waste and providing clear visual instructions.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The optimization will use a **Guillotine Cut Algorithm**, which is standard for saw-based operations where cuts must go from one edge to the other. This differs from "irregular nesting" used in CNC or laser cutting.

